rows.label: tlk70000138_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I'm from Iira. Born and
raised in the capital.

rows.label: tlk70000138_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Couldn't get on with my eccentric
dad, so I left home and became
a captain's apprentice.

rows.label: tlk70000138_02_msg0006
rows.name: The air's good in Gula, at least.

rows.label: tlk70000138_02_msg0007
rows.name:
Iira's got plenty of trees, but around
the capital it's mostly desert. Clouds
of sand don't make for good breathing.

rows.label: tlk70000138_02_msg0008
rows.name:
I like my new job. Means I
can go all sorts of places.
